----------------------------------------------------------------------
Models
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Maestria does NOT distribute any model weights. Users download GGUF /
safetensors model files themselves (typically from Hugging Face). Each
model carries its own license, which Maestria reads from the file
header / Hugging Face metadata and surfaces in the UI as a tag
(`lic:*`), but does not enforce. Compliance with each model's license
is the user's responsibility.
